1.0.0.name: wordpress/jne-tiki-tracking-for-wordpress
1.0.0.description:
JNE-TIKI Tracking for WordPress is a WordPress plugin that can integrate JNE / TIKI tracking into your online shopping website without leaving your own website. It's really simple and easy. You just need to put <!--jne-tiki-tracking--> into your post / page content to generate the form.
